ffi::c_str::CString::into_boxed_c_str.doc:
Converts this `CString` into a boxed [`CStr`].

# Examples

```
let c_string = c"foo".to_owned();
let boxed = c_string.into_boxed_c_str();
assert_eq!(boxed.to_bytes_with_nul(), b"foo\0");
```

